Detailed Description

cvmx_dlfe_sos_filter

Initial value of the SoS filter counter loaded when the SOS_DL is received from RFIF. Ths SoS filter counter decrments by one each clock cycle. If the next SOS_DL arrives before the counter reaches zero, then the SOS_DL is ignored.
